title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update IX Italy & Malta - Venice
description:
In this video we will have a look at Venice which has received a massive update as part of World Update IX. Both the photogrammetry content and the number of POI's have been improved. Based on a first look I think Venice received one of the most POI's per square meter which I have ever seen in MSFS.
